            "title": "谷歌加碼德州佈局 計畫投資400億美元建數據中心",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> Alphabet旗下谷歌計畫在德克薩斯州投資400億美元新建三座<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:數據中心;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/數據中心\">數據中心</a>，在OpenAI和 Anthropic PBC等競爭對手在該州推進數十億美元投資計畫時擴大自身佈局。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">谷歌周五在聲明中表示，這項投資將持續到2027年。其中一座數據中心將位於德州的Armstrong縣，另外兩座在Haskell縣。其中一處在Haskell的設施將與新建的太陽能與電池儲能設施共址，以減輕對電網的影響。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-0dace6d3-e2ee-3964-ab22-3bb64c3169a7-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「這項投資將創造數千個就業崗位，為大學生和電工學徒提供技能培訓，並加快德州各地能源可負擔性計畫的推進，」Alphabet執行長Sundar Pichai在達拉斯附近的活動上表示，該公司在當地已有兩處數據中心。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Google to Invest $40 Billion in New Data Centers in Texas (1)</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%B0%B7%E6%AD%8C%E5%8A%A0%E7%A2%BC%E5%BE%B7%E5%B7%9E%E4%BD%88%E5%B1%80-%E8%A8%88%E7%95%AB%E6%8A%95%E8%B3%87400%E5%84%84%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83%E5%BB%BA%E6%95%B8%E6%93%9A%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83-212734022.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-11-15 06:31:01",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "美國勞工統計局：9月非農就業報告將於11月20日發布",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 受之前的政府停擺影響，美國勞工統計局將把9月份就業報告推遲到下周四公佈。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在美國史上最長的政府停擺結束後，勞工統計局周五更新了經濟數據發布時間表。該機構還表示，將於11月21日公佈9月份經通膨調整後的工資數據。所有報告將在華盛頓時間上午8點30分發布。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這些報告相對容易重新安排發布，因為在政府停擺前，9月份就業報告的數據采集工作已完成。而實際工資數據通常與消費者物價指數(CPI)同步發布，後者在政府停擺期間被指示繼續公佈，以便社會保障局計算年度生活成本調整。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-603e9ffa-8ecb-3f50-949e-053cb849fce4-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">新數據將逐步揭示美國經濟的運行狀況，但相比往常會更具滯後性。雖然部分替代數據在停擺期間填補了一些空白，但在缺乏關鍵官方統計的情況下，政策制定者、企業高管和投資者在相當長時間內基本一直處於「盲飛」狀態。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">經濟學家和投資者目前密切關注的不僅是10月數據何時公佈，還有其發布形式。白宮國家經濟委員會主任凱文·哈塞特周四表示，10月份就業報告將不包括失業率，白宮確認不會發布10月份CPI報告。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">每月的就業報告由兩項調查構成，企業調查生成主要的非農就業人數數據，家庭調查則支撐失業率的計算。儘管多數企業會保留記錄並通過電子方式報告人力數據，但家庭調查需要統計人員通過電話聯繫調查對象並讓他們回憶10月某一特定周的就業狀態，這方面補采難度較大。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國人口普查局和經濟分析局尚未公佈包括零售銷售及經通膨調整的消費者支出等關鍵數據的更新時間。經濟分析局的許多報告依賴勞工統計局和普查局的數據，該分析局稱，正與這兩家機構及其他數據提供方協商，以確定數據可用性。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題BLS Says September US Jobs Report Will Be Released Nov. 20 (2)</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%8B%9E%E5%B7%A5%E7%B5%B1%E8%A8%88%E5%B1%80-9%E6%9C%88%E9%9D%9E%E8%BE%B2%E5%B0%B1%E6%A5%AD%E5%A0%B1%E5%91%8A%E5%B0%87%E6%96%BC11%E6%9C%8820%E6%97%A5%E7%99%BC%E5%B8%83-205022076.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-11-15 05:30:56",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "川普擬削減部分食品雜貨的關稅 緩解選民對物價的擔憂",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 據白宮官員透露，美國總統唐納德·川普計畫周五頒令下調牛肉、番茄、咖啡和香蕉的關稅。此舉旨在降低食品雜貨價格，回應選民要求降低日常用品價格的壓力。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這些豁免措施將降低對那些美國國內產量不足以滿足需求的商品的貿易關稅。關稅削減的具體範圍、涉及的商品數量以及適用程度尚不清楚。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">此舉正值川普將政策重點轉向提高負擔能力，因為選民對他領導下的經濟狀況日益感到擔憂。此舉也相當於默認了川普的關稅政策加大了美國消費者的價格壓力。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-94647f6a-5a75-3cac-8c9d-d22c8b041af9-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">白宮未立即回應置評請求。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">推薦閱讀：食品價格高企引發選民憤怒 美國將公佈關稅豁免措施</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Trump Set to Cut Tariffs on Beef, Tomatoes as Prices Vex Voters</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%B7%9D%E6%99%AE%E6%93%AC%E5%89%8A%E6%B8%9B%E9%83%A8%E5%88%86%E9%A3%9F%E5%93%81%E9%9B%9C%E8%B2%A8%E7%9A%84%E9%97%9C%E7%A8%85-%E7%B7%A9%E8%A7%A3%E9%81%B8%E6%B0%91%E5%B0%8D%E7%89%A9%E5%83%B9%E7%9A%84%E6%93%94%E6%86%82-193032691.html",
